message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product. It's worth more than $120 to us, but I understand its value might be different to you. To ensure we both benefit, I propose a price of $150 for this exceptional item. Let me know if this works for you or if you'd like to make a counteroffer.

Hello Alice, thank you for your offer. I appreciate the value of your product, but based on my needs and budget, I would like to propose a price of $120 for the product. I believe this aligns closely with its worth to me. I look forward to your response.
